    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS
) AS [t]

    SELECT [w].[Id], [w].[CategoryType], [w].[CreaDate], [w].[CreaUser], [w].[Definition], [w].[IsActive], [w].[IsDeleted], [w].[IsState], [w].[IsStatus], [w].[ModDate], [w].[ModUser], [w].[Name], [w].[OrderNo], [w].[PublishDate], [w].[PublishDuration]

) AS [t]

""SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[CategoryType], [t].[CreaDate], [t].[CreaUser], [t].[Definition], [t].[IsActive], [t].[IsDeleted], [t].[IsState], [t].[IsStatus], [t].[ModDate], [t].[ModUser], [t].[Name], [t].[OrderNo], [t].[PublishDate], [t].[PublishDuration], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CreaDate], [t0].[CreaUser], [t0].[Definition], [t0].[IsActive], [t0].[IsDeleted], [t0].[IsState], [t0].[IsStatus], [t0].[ModDate], [t0].[ModUser], [t0].[Name], [t0].[OrderNo], [t0].[WorkshopId]

    SELECT [w].[Id], [w].[CategoryType], [w].[CreaDate], [w].[CreaUser], [w].[Definition], [w].[IsActive], [w].[IsDeleted], [w].[IsState], [w].[IsStatus], [w].[ModDate], [w].[ModUser], [w].[Name], [w].[OrderNo], [w].[PublishDate], [w].[PublishDuration]

    ORDER BY (SELECT 1)
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS
) AS [t]

""SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[CategoryType], [t].[CreaDate], [t].[CreaUser], [t].[Definition], [t].[IsActive], [t].[IsDeleted], [t].[IsState], [t].[IsStatus], [t].[ModDate], [t].[ModUser], [t].[Name], [t].[OrderNo], [t].[PublishDate], [t].[PublishDuration], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CreaDate], [t0].[CreaUser], [t0].[Definition], [t0].[IsActive], [t0].[IsDeleted], [t0].[IsState], [t0].[IsStatus], [t0].[ModDate], [t0].[ModUser], [t0].[Name], [t0].[OrderNo], [t0].[WorkshopId]

2021-02-10 01:36:05.478 +03:00 [Information] [Microsoft.EntityFrameworkCore.Database.Command] [{ Id: 20101, Name: "Microsoft.EntityFrameworkCore.Database.Command.CommandExecuted" }] Executed DbCommand ("151"ms) [Parameters=["@__id_0='?' (DbType = Int32)"], CommandType='Text', CommandTimeout='30']"
""SELECT TOP(1) [c].[Id], [c].[ContentData], [c].[CreaDate], [c].[CreaUser], [c].[DocVideoDesc], [c].[DocumentType], [c].[IsActive], [c].[IsDeleted], [c].[IsState], [c].[IsStatus], [c].[ModDate], [c].[ModUser], [c].[OrderNo], [c].[ResponseType], [c].[SectionId], [c].[VideoLink], [t].[Id], [t].[CreaDate], [t].[CreaUser], [t].[Definition], [t].[IsActive], [t].[IsDeleted], [t].[IsState], [t].[IsStatus], [t].[ModDate], [t].[ModUser], [t].[Name], [t].[OrderNo], [t].[WorkshopId]
FROM [Content] AS [c]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT [s].[Id], [s].[CreaDate], [s].[CreaUser], [s].[Definition], [s].[IsActive], [s].[IsDeleted], [s].[IsState], [s].[IsStatus], [s].[ModDate], [s].[ModUser], [s].[Name], [s].[OrderNo], [s].[WorkshopId]
    FROM [Section] AS [s]
    WHERE [s].[IsDeleted] IS NULL
) AS [t] ON [c].[SectionId] = [t].[Id]
WHERE [c].[IsDeleted] IS NULL AND ([c].[Id] = @__id_0)"

""SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[ContentData], [t].[CreaDate], [t].[CreaUser], [t].[DocVideoDesc], [t].[DocumentType], [t].[IsActive], [t].[IsDeleted], [t].[IsState], [t].[IsStatus], [t].[ModDate], [t].[ModUser], [t].[OrderNo], [t].[ResponseType], [t].[SectionId], [t].[VideoLink], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CreaDate], [t0].[CreaUser], [t0].[Definition], [t0].[IsActive], [t0].[IsDeleted], [t0].[IsState], [t0].[IsStatus], [t0].[ModDate], [t0].[ModUser], [t0].[Name], [t0].[OrderNo], [t0].[WorkshopId]
FROM (
    SELECT [c].[Id], [c].[ContentData], [c].[CreaDate], [c].[CreaUser], [c].[DocVideoDesc], [c].[DocumentType], [c].[IsActive], [c].[IsDeleted], [c].[IsState], [c].[IsStatus], [c].[ModDate], [c].[ModUser], [c].[OrderNo], [c].[ResponseType], [c].[SectionId], [c].[VideoLink]

    WHERE [c].[IsDeleted] IS NULL AND ([c].[SectionId] = @__selectid_0)
    ORDER BY (SELECT 1)
    OFFSET @__p_1 ROWS
) AS [t]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT [s].[Id], [s].[CreaDate], [s].[CreaUser], [s].[Definition], [s].[IsActive], [s].[IsDeleted], [s].[IsState], [s].[IsStatus], [s].[ModDate], [s].[ModUser], [s].[Name], [s].[OrderNo], [s].[WorkshopId]

    WHERE [s].[IsDeleted] IS NULL
) AS [t] ON [c].[SectionId] = [t].[Id]
WHERE [c].[IsDeleted] IS NULL AND ([c].[Id] = @__id_0)"

""SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[CategoryType], [t].[CreaDate], [t].[CreaUser], [t].[Definition], [t].[IsActive], [t].[IsDeleted], [t].[IsState], [t].[IsStatus], [t].[ModDate], [t].[ModUser], [t].[Name], [t].[OrderNo], [t].[PublishDate], [t].[PublishDuration], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CreaDate], [t0].[CreaUser], [t0].[Definition], [t0].[IsActive], [t0].[IsDeleted], [t0].[IsState], [t0].[IsStatus], [t0].[ModDate], [t0].[ModUser], [t0].[Name], [t0].[OrderNo], [t0].[WorkshopId]
